{"hash":"ca8e09572798bf91f5f3bbc7e6778eb71ce4f282","data":{"post":{"title":"Dag 1 - Wenen, Oostenrijk","author":"","date":"2016-11-18","content":"<p>Dachten we lekker snel weg te kunnen vanuit Rotterdam Airport, hebben we toch nog twee uur vertraging gehad.. Goed begin.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00419-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00419\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Na landing direct naar ons hotel gegaan. Lekker geslapen, helaas geen foto van de kamer gemaakt. In de morgen opzoek naar ontbijt. Lekker bij de supermarkt verse broodjes.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00428-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00428\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Nu onderweg naar het centrum. Stadpark.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00450-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00450\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00444-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00444\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>En een mannetje die aan een klok hangt..</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00462-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00462\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Kerstmarkt nr. 01!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00552-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00552\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Dit is chocolade! Net echt.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00536-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00536\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00557-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00557\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Even een tussendoortje.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00520-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00520\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161119_104558-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161119_104558\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Rathaus.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00573-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00573\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Domkirche St. St6ephan</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//WhatsApp-Image-2016-12-12-at-20.20.42-1024x995.jpeg\" alt=\"whatsapp-image-2016-12-12-at-20-20-42\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Tijd voor lunch! Lekker bratwurst met patatjes en vegetarische dumplings.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00588-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00588\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00590-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00590\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Kerstmarkt nr. 02!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00619-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00619\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//WhatsApp-Image-2016-12-12-at-20.15.33-1024x576.jpeg\" alt=\"whatsapp-image-2016-12-12-at-20-15-33\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161119_113043-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161119_113043\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Naschmarcht</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161119_152537-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161119_152537\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161119_153245-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161119_153245\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161119_152555-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161119_152555\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Kerstmarkt nr 03!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161119_154811-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161119_154811\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//20161119_154705-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"20161119_154705\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Het avondeten, lekker sushi en duck ramen!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00611-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00611\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00609-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00609\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>En verder de kerstmarkten bezoeken.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00643-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00643\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00637-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00637\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00634-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00634\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads//DSC00626-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"dsc00626\" class=\"img-fluid\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","id":"a23a52fa6802c3a3cf316105066770a2","path":"/blog/oostenrijk-2016/dag-1-wenen-oostenrijk/","image":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/DSC00419.jpg","category":{"title":"Wenen - Oostenrijk","id":"Wenen - Oostenrijk","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"Dag 1 - Wenen, Oostenrijk","path":"/blog/oostenrijk-2016/dag-1-wenen-oostenrijk/","id":"a23a52fa6802c3a3cf316105066770a2","excerpt":"Dachten we lekker snel weg te kunnen vanuit Rotterdam Airport, hebben we toch nog twee uur vertraging gehad.. Goed begin."}},{"node":{"title":"Day 2 - Wenen, Oostenrijk","path":"/blog/oostenrijk-2016/day-2-wenen-oostenrijk/","id":"de07680837343d12f23306bf02855180","excerpt":"Lekker beginnen met een goed ontbijt..."}}]}}}},"context":{}}